{"word":"G1729 - ἐνδεής - endeḗs - en-deh-ace' - Lacking","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐνδεής</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">endeḗs</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">en-deh-ace'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Lacking</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தேவையான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"needy, destitute"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From a compound of <a href=\"#/G1722 - ἐν - en - en/1722\">G1722</a> and <a href=\"#/G1210 - δέω - déō - deh'-o/1210\">G1210</a> (in the sense of <i>lacking</i>); <i>deficient in:</i> - lacking.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}